latestIgtvVideos.title: In my skin ♥️- to everyone who needs to love themselves a little more.
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
How often do you find yourself looking at your reflection and feeling, ‘this is me in my own skin; this is my body and this is who I am? Society is built on fiction and perhaps, the biggest myth about the social human body is that it is always supposed to be lacking – it is supposed to be ‘too fat’, ‘too loose’, ‘too skinny’, and never enough. The idea behind this film is to not tell you that you’re beautiful in your own way, whatever way might be – instead, it is to remind you that you are beautiful simply by virtue of being in your skin and that all it takes is the courage to realise that we are all navigating our relationship with our bodies through similar versions of those fictions. Kindness to ourselves and our fellow passengers on the boat is the only way through. <3

Presenting IN MY SKIN, a film by Homegrown.
